node.text:
We are excited to introduce our Brewing for Diversity Scholarship initiative in partnership with @ucsdextension and their brewing program! Ballast Point will grant one scholarship per year, and recipients will be selected by partner team members and the @sdbrewers Guild Inclusion Committee. We can’t wait to support YOU and a more inclusive brewing community. 

Visit the link in our bio for more information on how to apply!

node.text: Did you know Sculpin IPA was a recipe blend? Learn more about our iconic, award-winning IPA from the original brewers and our longtime label artist.

node.text:
Past ➡ Present

Go ahead and mix it up with us 🍻 #25yearsinbeer

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Ballast Point Brewing Co. in San Diego, California. May be an image of drink and outdoors.

node.text:
Today is a very good day 🍻 ⚾️

Our latest rendition of Pinstripe Lager is crisp and lightly-hopped with notes of citrus and nectar fruits. Motueka hops balance the maltiness with a soft bitterness. It's that post-homerun swag in a can.

Limited edition 16oz 6-packs will be available beginning 8/6 at our Home Brew Mart, Little Italy, and Miramar tasting rooms, while supplies last!

node.text:
Rolling right into IPA Days 🤙🏽😎

August 2 - August 8 we will be celebrating IPA Days in style with a special menu of small batch IPAs on draft in all of our Tasting Rooms! 🍻

To make it even more special we're also throwing in a sweet deal on our Sculpin family of brews! Snag a case of Sculpin, Grapefruit Sculpin, or Aloha Sculpin bottles only for $25 🙌🏽

While supplies last. Four cases max per customer. Explore responsibly.
